room_title: Escape room "Death at a Funeral" by Tactical Escape 101 in Minneapolis - St. Paul
room_description: Death at a Funeral! Sir Arthur Conan Doyle has been MURDERED and Sherlock is just not himself without him. (!fter-all SCAD is Sherlock’s Author) Help Sherlock solve the murder, stay alive yourself and catch the culprit! Here’s the twist, One of the players (you) are the killer and no one will know who until it is over! The murder will walk away labeled for life and will get a special gift only available to one player per adventure. Do you have what it takes…. to be accused of MURDER????
